Description: Text mode RSS feed newsreader
DescDetail: <<
Snownews is a text mode RSS/RDF newsreader. It supports RSS 1.0 feeds that comply with the W3C RDF specification and also supports 
Radio Userland's RSS 0.91 and 2.0 versions.

Fast and very resource friendly.
Bultin HTTP client will follow server redirects and update feed URLs that point to permanent redirects (301) automatically.
Snownews understands \"Not-Modified\" (304) server replies and handles gzip/deflate Content-Encoding
Local cache for minimal network traffic
HTTP proxy support
A help menu available throughout the program
Automatic update checking (can be deactivated)
Import feature for OPML subscription lists
Fully customizable key bindings of all program functions
Type Ahead Find for quick and easy navigation
<<
